ABOUT PAD OPTIMAL*
A pad-optimal rig, as defined by the E & P industry, consists of four key drilling and two key moving attributes that are essential in helping 
operators reduce cycle times and operating costs on their most challenging and complex horizontal drilling programs. These attributes include:1500HP, Bi-fuel capable, High pressure mud systems, AC VFD Drive, Omni-directional walking system, and the ability to undertake fast conventional rig moves safely and efficiently.


FOR MORE INFORMATION
  

For additional information on our ShaleDrillerÂŽ rigs or to request a proposal for drilling services, please email us 
at salesmanager@icdrilling.com.








