SHALEDRILLER®
RIG LOCATOR
TECHNICAL LIBRARY



ShaleDriller® series rigs are fast moving, programmable AC rigs custom designed to be best in class for the development of shale plays and other areas where completions require long horizontal sections.


ShaleDriller 1500 HP 



Drawworks


-
1500 Drawworks  powered by (1) 1500HP AC Motor




Mast and Substructure


-
Hydraulically Raised  Mast 143’ Height 750,000 lbs Hook Load


-
Hydraulically Raised  “Single Load” Substructure 26 ft height, 22.5 ft RBC


-
750,000 lbs Rotary Capacity, 500,000 lbs Setback Capacity


-
200 Series: (4) fully integrated and independent, multidirectional, hydraulic, “WALKING” system


-
200 Series: 120 ft. telescoping flow line custom engineered for multi-well “WALKING” pad applications





Mud Pumps


-
(2) 1500  Triplex Pumps


-
(1) each A/C 1500 HP Motors




 Rotating and Traveling Equipment


-
500 ton Top Drive drilling system, with 37,500 ft-lbs Torque @ 110 rpm


-
ICD 27-1/2” Rotary Table Independent Drive powered by (1) 1150 AC Motor


-
500 ton Traveling Block




B.O.P. Equipment


-
BOP Handling System


-
13-5/8” X 5000 psi Annular


-
13-5/8” x 10,000 psi, single Ram BOP


-
13 5/8” x 10,000 psi, Double Ram BOP


-
2-1/16” X 4-1/16” 10,000 psi Choke Manifold


-
(1) 6 station accumulator skid




Generators


-
(3) Diesel Engines w/(3) 1750 kVa Kato Gen. Sets


-
(3) Bi-Fuel (natural gas/diesel) package (1 per engine)




VFD House


-
ICD ShaleDriller AC/VFD House




Mud Systems


-
(3) pit 1000 bbl. circulating mud system


-
(2) linear motion shale shakers


-
(1) 16 cone desilter


-
(1) 3 cone desander


-
(1) Vacu-Flo 1200 vacuum degasser


-
(1) mud gas separator 1200 gpm 48” diameter and 16’ overall length


-
All solids control equipment mounted on a one-load hydraulically raised skid




