Independence Contract Drilling, Inc. and each of its subsidiaries ("ICD") is an equal opportunity employer. We do not discriminate on the basis of race, religion, national origin, color, sex, age, or disability. It is our intent that all applicants be given equal opportunity with selection decisions based on job-related factors.


