I understand that this application does not create a contract of employment, obligate ICD to offer me employment or to hire me.  I further understand that if I am employed by ICD, my employment will be on at “AT WILL” basis and may be terminated by ICD at any time with or without cause or notice.  If I am employed, I understand that I will wear all required personal protection equipment and will abide by all federal, state, local, laws and ICD procedures and regulations while working for ICD.
In connection with my application for employment with ICD, I understand that investigational background inquires may be conducted on me including consumer, criminal, driving, and industrial safety records.  These reports will include, but no be limited to, information regarding my character, work habits, performance, and experience along with reasons for termination of employment with previous employers.  I acknowledge that I have been provided with a summary of my rights relating to a consumer background investigation and that I have authorized ICD to conduct a consumer background investigation on me. Further, I understand that information from various federal, state, and local agencies may be requested regarding my past activities relating to driving, credit, criminal and civil litigation, as well as claims involving me in the records of insurance companies.  I agree to submit to medical testing including a physical examination and drug and alcohol testing.   
I understand that failure to submit to any of these tests or an unsatisfactory result from any of these tests will disqualify me from further consideration for employment with ICD. Please submit application to HR@icdrilling.com for review. 

