 (1) 
 In the second quarter of 2017, we recorded a $0.5 million, or $0.02 per share, non-cash impairment reflecting the estimated loss from the expected sale of our Galayda facility.  In the first quarter of 2017, we recorded a $0.1 million, or $0.01 per share, non-cash impairment representing the estimated damage to the mast of one of our rigs, net of insurance recoveries.   


 (2) 
