Account Management Has Increased Its Blackstone Group L.P. (BX) Position, Independence Contract Drilling (ICD)’s Sentiment Is 1.82


					
						July 27, 2017 - By Louis Casey

 About 88,785 shares traded. Independence Contract Drilling Inc (ICD) has risen 7.92% since July 27, 2016 and is uptrending. It has underperformed by 8.78% the S&P500.







Account Management Llc increased Blackstone Group L.P. (BX) stake by 16.19% reported in 2016Q4 SEC filing. Account Management Llc acquired 24,850 shares as Blackstone Group L.P. (BX)’s stock declined 1.16%. The Account Management Llc holds 178,330 shares with $4.82M value, up from 153,480 last quarter. Blackstone Group L.P. now has $40.52B valuation. The stock declined 0.38% or $0.13 reaching $33.82 on the news. About 1.93 million shares traded. Blackstone Group LP (NYSE:BX) has risen 20.49% since July 27, 2016 and is uptrending. It has outperformed by 3.79% the S&P500.
Lime Rock Management Lp holds 100% of its portfolio in Independence Contract Drilling Inc for 1.53 million shares. Scoria Capital Partners Lp owns 707,170 shares or 7.13% of their US portfolio. Moreover, Napier Park Global Capital (Us) Lp has 5.24% invested in the company for 230,000 shares. The Isle Of Man-based Oceanic Investment Management Ltd has invested 1.6% in the stock. Viking Fund Management Llc, a North Dakota-based fund reported 500,000 shares.
Among 17 analysts covering The Blackstone Group L.P. (NYSE:BX), 13 have Buy rating, 0 Sell and 4 Hold. Therefore 76% are positive. The Blackstone Group L.P. had 49 analyst reports since August 9, 2015 according to SRatingsIntel. Bank of America downgraded the shares of BX in report on Tuesday, December 8 to “Neutral” rating. The rating was maintained by Argus Research on Tuesday, October 27 with “Buy”. The firm earned “Buy” rating on Friday, September 18 by Deutsche Bank. The firm earned “Buy” rating on Thursday, July 20 by Oppenheimer. JMP Securities maintained the shares of BX in report on Thursday, July 20 with “Buy” rating. The rating was maintained by RBC Capital Markets on Thursday, October 22 with “Outperform”. The rating was maintained by Jefferies on Wednesday, June 28 with “Buy”. The firm earned “Buy” rating on Friday, January 8 by Deutsche Bank. Deutsche Bank maintained Blackstone Group LP (NYSE:BX) rating on Monday, August 17. Deutsche Bank has “Buy” rating and $48 target. Citigroup upgraded Blackstone Group LP (NYSE:BX) on Monday, May 22 to “Buy” rating.
Investors sentiment decreased to 1 in Q4 2016. Its down 0.28, from 1.28 in 2016Q3. It fall, as 33 investors sold BX shares while 156 reduced holdings. 45 funds opened positions while 144 raised stakes. 272.04 million shares or 1.58% more from 267.82 million shares in 2016Q3 were reported. Coe Cap Mgmt Limited Liability Corp reported 14,120 shares stake. The New York-based Pinnacle Assoc has invested 0.09% in Blackstone Group LP (NYSE:BX). Martin Currie Limited has 0.29% invested in Blackstone Group LP (NYSE:BX). Jrm Invest Counsel Ltd Liability Com invested 3.33% in Blackstone Group LP (NYSE:BX). Moreover, Caldwell And Orkin has 1.09% invested in Blackstone Group LP (NYSE:BX). The Florida-based Provise Management Ltd Liability Corp has invested 0.15% in Blackstone Group LP (NYSE:BX). Bryn Mawr Trust holds 0.02% or 9,600 shares in its portfolio. Btc Capital invested 0.35% in Blackstone Group LP (NYSE:BX). Thompson Davis And reported 700 shares stake. Parsons Cap Mgmt Inc Ri invested 0.08% in Blackstone Group LP (NYSE:BX). M&R Mgmt accumulated 2,000 shares or 0.01% of the stock. Cibc Mkts Incorporated has 0.01% invested in Blackstone Group LP (NYSE:BX). Polar Capital Llp invested in 0.1% or 235,817 shares. Kcm Investment Ltd Liability Co owns 33,496 shares. The Tennessee-based Delta Asset Mngmt Lc Tn has invested 0% in Blackstone Group LP (NYSE:BX).
Since February 8, 2017, it had 0 insider buys, and 4 insider sales for $21.50 million activity. Shares for $614,400 were sold by Finley John G. Solotar Joan also sold $1.02 million worth of Blackstone Group LP (NYSE:BX) on Monday, June 5. Goodman Bennett J also sold $19.22 million worth of Blackstone Group LP (NYSE:BX) shares.








